@Koca114
First I had this big update which worked, but now I got this little update which wont work (unable to find version number). What I do is just click "No" everytime it asks for update, and I disabled the Uplay in-game overlay, and accepted all the FarCry .exes in my firewall.

So now everytime I open it comes up an update which I decline and the game starts :)
